<concept id="concept_E8D43EB4494E41D2AB42D4A89396D1AB"
                    xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Distribution Media</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p><i><b>PENDING</b>: Distribution media for CMM 2.0 to be defined and agreed upon with FJJ. Section to be rewritten.</i></p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <p><ph conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> is distributed in the <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> installation package. It contains the <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> software and documentation for installing and configuring <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/>. </p>
            <p>The package includes:<ul>
                    <li>
                        <p><codeph>CMM_server_2.0.0_images.tar</codeph>:</p>
                        <p>## file used for setting up the docker images required for installing <ph
                                conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/></p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><codeph>.env</codeph>:</p>
                        <p>Docker Compose configuration file for setting up the <ph
                                conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> installer.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><codeph>docker-compose-metrics.yml</codeph> and <codeph>docker-compose-log.yml</codeph>:</p>
                        <p>Docker Compose files for setting up and running the Docker containers required for <ph
                                conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/>.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><codeph>monasca-agent-2.0.0.run</codeph>:</p>
                        <p>Executable for installing a Metrics Agent on the OpenStack platform.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><codeph>log-agent-2.0.0.run</codeph>:</p>
                        <p>Executable for installing a Log Agent on an OpenStack node.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><codeph>monasca-ui-2.0.0.run</codeph>:</p>
                        <p>Executable for installing the Horizon Plugin on the OpenStack platform.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><codeph>Manuals</codeph> subdirectory:</p>
                        <p>PDF manuals providing an overview of <ph
                                conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                            /> as well as information directed to system operators and application operators.</p>
                    </li>
                </ul></p>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
         
            
            
            
            
